        "action": "Introduce 'Skye's Law': Require all sex offenders to stay on register for life",
        "additional_details": "This should help to cut down crimes against children and teenagers that face sexual abuse. More needs to be done and more needs to tackle this.",
        "background": "The Government should introduce \u2018Skye\u2019s Law\u2019 to require that all convicted sex offenders are placed on the sex offenders register for life, not for ten years or less as is currently the case for certain offences. ",
